Open `.gitattributes` in VS Code and paste this:
```
# Handle line endings automatically
* text=auto

# Force these file types to always use LF
*.py    text eol=lf
*.md    text eol=lf
*.toml  text eol=lf
*.txt   text eol=lf

# Force these to always use CRLF on Windows
*.bat   text eol=crlf
*.cmd   text eol=crlf
```
This configuration ensures that line endings are handled correctly across different operating systems, preventing issues with inconsistent line endings in your project.